        <h3>Application Flow</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Entry Point</strong> main.js</li>
            <li><strong>main.js [Main]</strong> Init Application, Routes, Backbone History and Register listener to
                links
            </li>
            <li><strong>app.js [Application]</strong> Config Backbone Layouts and Render them according to routes</li>
            <li><strong>router.js [Router]</strong> Register 3 routes and provide Application with the Layout to render
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
